adudecalledleo.lionutils

Class IdentifierFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • adudecalledleo.lionutils.IdentifierFactory

  • public class IdentifierFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Constructs Identifiers in a single namespace. Ensures that identifiers with the same path are identical.
    A must-have for content mods.
